<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>49</hymn_number>
<title>OH COME, ALLYE FAITHFUL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw hung un, muonumte,
 Guolzo a kipak in;
 Beth-lehem zuon in kitawn dieldiel hitiu;
 En in, gankuong ah,
 Angelte Leng a kuol

[V2]
 Aw, hung un, chawian hitiu (3)
 Lal Krista.

[V3]
 2. Angelte, la sau in,
 Zawhna la go sau in;
 Na la sak un van a Angelte thawng hen,
 I Pathien kawm ah,
 Chungnungpen lopi hen,

[V4]
 Aw, hung un, chawian hitiu, (3)
 Lal Krista.

[V5]
 3. Amen, vangphat chang in,
 Ka damna diu a pieng;
 Aw Isu, kumkhuo'n Na min chawihat hi hen,
 Pa Pathien Thu chuh,
 Taksa a hung pieng chuh;

[V6]
 Aw, hung un, chawian hitiu, (3)
 Lal Krista.</lyrics>
</song>